OL,4,CPsychedelic therapy could 'reset'
OL,5,Cdepressed brain
OL,6, A powerful hallucinogenic drug known
OL,7, for its part in shamanic rituals is
OL,8, being trialled as a potential cure for
OL,9, depression for the first time.
OL,11,FParticipants will be given the drug
OL,12,FDMT, followed by talking therapy.
OL,14,FIt is hoped this could offer an
OL,15,Falternative for the significant number
OL,16,Fof people who don't respond to
OL,17,Fconventional pills for depression.
OL,19,FPsychedelic-assisted therapy might
OL,20,Foffer longer-term relief from symptoms,
OL,21,Fsome researchers believe.
